
Use git commands to remove the file
===================================
git rm file.txt

It removed the file and staged it & then we can commit it

Rename the tracked file
================================
git mv first.txt first_name.txt

It renamed the file and staged it & then we can commit it

Git ignore
=========================
When we mention any untracked file or dir in gitignore file the git will ignore those files or untrack it
but when a tracked file is mentioned in git ignore the git will still try to track it
Use below command to remove file from tracked  to untracked status
git rm --cached file.txt


